Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}好萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是博士喵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是博士喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲家 今天也很和諧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}好萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球為什麼是圓的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭為什麼能飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼磁鐵能互相吸引呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上的東西 全部都能用科學證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:19.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(867,553)}墳\N墓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們討論的死後的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈、鬼故事之類的靈異現象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種令人想睡覺的東西怎麼可能有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不可以有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈者 根本不能信！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7}イタコ{\r\fs36}：日本東北一種能招魂的巫女，多弱視；青森縣的恐山夏季舉行的遊客\N現場聆聽通靈者招魂的恐山大祭很出名；通靈王中的恐山安娜就是一名{\fs30\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7}イタコ{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了八小時踏上了恐山的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著越來越接近山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的躍動也愈加強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有通靈者麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的話在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人住在這種地方麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1075,463)}通\N靈\N者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊讓她召喚一次試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚一下石鹼吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是石鹼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克測試 麥克測試 滋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克測試 測試 測試 滋 滋滋滋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這種完全沒有辦法的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 真有叫「石鹼」的這麼個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試 測試 測試 滋 滋 噓 噓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 哈 石 石 石鹼 石鹼 石鹼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石鹼 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問些什麼的話 肯定會出現一些矛盾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石鹼是什麼血型的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 誰知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫一些簡單的人物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信長 召喚一下織田信長吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召不召喚之前就拒絕了這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 多少也是上了年紀的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有健康狀況的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因為這個責怪她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無法責怪別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是明白這一點 不也是一種收穫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五千元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:24.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95\pos(1095,150)}雪\N飄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:24.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs27\pos(1173,150)}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:31.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(100,360)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&}敲\N不\N倒\N翁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不是說明過了麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了的話就要敲對方啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狠哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狠的做法哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從另一個層面說比敲我更過分哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了哦 就像剛才說明的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的話就要防禦 贏了的話就要敲對方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\c&H86F8FB&\3c&H000000&\bord2\shad0\b1\frz353.178\pos(1167,185)}猛擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在打你妹啊！ 為毛現在打我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 剛才不是贏了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是現在 是剛才！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那個瞬間哦 就那個瞬間生效哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是那種生物哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清零重新開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁是零啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑啊 沒想到是個小丑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上的打擊 也是有的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我說 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 那個 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我還以為重生過來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個 放這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺 她好像非常高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那種東西怎麼樣都可以啦 繼續吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 石頭 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是石剪布嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\3c&H000000&\bord2\shad0\b1\pos(1201,221)\c&H8CF4F6&}暴擊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼… 這麼殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不帶的哦 不帶的 不帶石剪布的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後也不帶用佛像敲的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 就是這樣哦麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真是的 你這不是也可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 繼續了哦 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 先出 石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs33}Gascoigne貌似是人名，加斯科因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOD IS DEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 為什麼打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 剛才玩的不是好好的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒菩薩 可以借我看看麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我去圖書館還書去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fs24\c&H525351&\pos(135,594)}雪糕\N果汁\N不能吃\N太多哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs24\c&HB8ECE0&\pos(1073,623)}鯊魚型的巧克力\N為什麼這麼好吃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼名乃的不倒翁只有一個眼睛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦 博士把眼睛好好畫上去的話 說不定會被誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定 名乃會說吃好多點心也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是名乃的 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定 會被罵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}博士暫時不許吃點心！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這樣 這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊這是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼了啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是那小姑娘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 沒有眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照我說的辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 阪本先生你要出去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選新借的書 所以回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 博士 怎麼回事啊 你的肚子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒嘿 嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿 誒嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是「誒嘿嘿」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對 不可能這麼回事吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我要生了！我要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 啊 是什麼遊戲麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 名乃的弟弟要生出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:30.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(750,360)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&}狐\N狗\N狸\N先\N生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來玩「狐狗狸先生」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 美緒你竟然不知道啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就 稍微給你說明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 準備一張像這樣 在正中間畫一個鳥居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}鳥居：神社入口的牌坊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫著「是」和「不是」還有五十音圖的紙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的地方也有給神畫上油炸豆腐比較好的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}譯註：日本人普遍認為狐狸愛吃油炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只畫最簡單的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 為了讓狐狗狸先生能夠進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把北邊的窗子開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 把這個十元硬幣 放在這個鳥居的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起把手指放上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問想問的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的秘密 喜歡的人的事情 煩惱的事情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 明明什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十元硬幣卻自己來回動 狐狗狸先生會回答你的問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有幾條禁止事項
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 不能自己一個人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 不能開玩笑的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會被低級妖怪盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 中途停止的話也會被盯上的 一定要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個感覺 還是一個挺有危險的遊戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們來玩玩試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～咧～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那麼今天就這樣結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要進行小測驗 大家要好好學習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 延期吧 延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫不管怎麼延期結果都一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\c&HE5FBE2&\pos(265,545)}小\N測\N驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事想問…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於之前做的那個測試的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個是FLY哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 不是想問答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好像會被抹殺光線消滅的小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs33\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7}ニフラム{\r\fs36}：勇者鬥惡龍中用光束抹殺敵人的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老師你畫的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得如果放點畫上去的話 考試會變得溫柔一些之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師畫的畫很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我畫畫很差的 很難理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老師 下一次把我畫的畫放上去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會畫一些超帥的畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快聽 快聽 我畫的話要放到考試裡面去哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說會給我放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒現在也開始畫的畫 說不定會全都放上去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是全都放上去還是會漏一些的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 你不畫麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我就算了吧 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕緊把這個還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我來畫一筆帥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學畫畫真好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人敬仰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我啊 厲害吧 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提名字就叫做「五月雨喬治」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚啊 更加更加帥了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般說的帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord0\shad0\frz21\pos(408,413)\c&H767378&}憂\N鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像漫畫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長野原同學 你有在畫漫畫什麼的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有 就一點點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 下次請給我看看喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那可有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 不可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看 請給我看看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 啊 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借我一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的會更帥的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\bord0\shad0\c&H767378&\frz324.472\pos(442,255)}憂\N\N鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是抄襲麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有抄襲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是抄襲哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫抄襲的致敬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的都可以嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這樣的怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又知性又酷的形象到哪個時代都是女性的憧憬對象！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 眼鏡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不太好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴隱形眼鏡不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群人完全不能理解我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架在耳朵下面了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你這也是抄襲吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是太陽鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帥~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差別對待啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這樣子如何！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從迎接到泡紅茶 已經讓人有千金小姐的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受大吉嶺的魔力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}大吉嶺：指大吉嶺紅茶 印度大吉嶺地區產的紅茶 被譽為「茶中香檳」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 啊 還是眼鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我看不太懂這種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽隱形眼鏡的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒你不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 真正的帥氣這個東西是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 給我等等 這貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑著呢麼！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很快 好帥啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太扯了——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣這種東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣這種東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣這種東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符合常識… 符合常識的考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣這種東西是——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦～
