Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊聽爵士樂邊畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老師 您早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是老師啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來發一下早晨小測的卷子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家傳一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想將畫畫這件事情保密來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然畫出來那種畫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我暴走了 但只停留在那個級別的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是不幸中的萬幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能想著勉強還算好事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 兩三天之內會被小祐一直嘲笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 要忘記這個問題 向前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒老師 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 初次見面哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是擬聲詞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42\fn方正少兒_GBK}英：Onomatopoeia 法：Onomatopee
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cock-a-doodle-doo是讓人很想說的日語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是日語
